---
const { skill } = Astro.props;
---
<div class="v-teach">
  <div class="tc-head">
    <span class="tc-badge">Lesson 3</span>
    <span class="tc-topic">Database indexing</span>
  </div>
  <p class="tc-mission"><span class="tc-mlabel">Mission</span> Make the slow <code>WHERE email = ?</code> query fast — and understand <em>why</em> it was slow.</p>
  <div class="tc-glossary">
    <div class="tc-term">
      <span class="tc-word">B-tree index</span>
      <p class="tc-def">A sorted tree the DB walks to find rows in <code>O(log n)</code> instead of scanning all of them. Great for equality and range lookups.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tc-term">
      <span class="tc-word">Selectivity</span>
      <p class="tc-def">How well a column narrows the search. <code>email</code> is high (nearly unique); <code>is_active</code> is low — an index on it barely helps.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="tc-progress">
    <span class="tc-plabel">Learning record</span>
    <span class="tc-bar"><i style="width:60%"></i></span>
    <span class="tc-pnum">3 / 5 checkpoints</span>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .v-teach {
    padding: 26px; background: #faf9f6; color: #17150f;
    font-family: var(--font-sans, system-ui); border-radius: 10px;
  }
  .tc-head { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .tc-badge { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10.5px; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; background: #35507a; color: #fff; padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 4px; }
  .tc-topic { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 12px; color: #8f897b; letter-spacing: .03em; }
  .tc-mission { margin: 0 0 18px; font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.45; color: #201d16; }
  .tc-mlabel { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #35507a; margin-right: 8px; vertical-align: 2px; }
  .tc-mission code { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 14px; background: #eef0f4; color: #35507a; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 4px; }
  .tc-glossary { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .tc-term { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e7e3d8; border-radius: 9px; padding: 13px 15px; }
  .tc-word { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; color: #221f18; display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .tc-def { margin: 0; font-size: 12.5px; line-height: 1.5; color: #5b564a; }
  .tc-def code { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11.5px; background: #efece3; color: #7a4a2e; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px; }
  .tc-progress { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; padding-top: 4px; }
  .tc-plabel { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10.5px; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #8f897b; }
  .tc-bar { flex: 1; height: 7px; background: #e5e1d6; border-radius: 999px; overflow: hidden; }
  .tc-bar i { display: block; height: 100%; background: #35507a; border-radius: 999px; }
  .tc-pnum { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11.5px; color: #35507a; font-weight: 600; }
</style>
